    Title: I Ching
  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
Title: Acquiring Experience
---
The man is tolerant of the ignorant and kind to women. He resembles an
official capable of assuming the delegated duties of a prince in directing
a large social body with inner strength and outward reserve.
